{"blocks": [{"type": "html", "html": "<section class=\"flex flex-col gap-2\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-2\"><h1 class=\"text-[1.75em] font-semibold flex items-center gap-2\">Prompt Input<span class=\"chip chip--default chip--primary h-5 rounded-full bg-pink-400/8 px-1.5 text-[10px] font-semibold text-pink-400/90 w-fit\" data-slot=\"chip\"><span class=\"chip__label\" data-slot=\"chip-label\">New</span></span></h1><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"button-group button-group--horizontal\" data-slot=\"button-group\" data-rac=\"\" role=\"group\"><button data-slot=\"button\" class=\"button button--md button--tertiary\" data-rac=\"\" type=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" data-react-aria-pressable=\"true\" id=\"react-aria-_R_cminpfsnmknb_\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"1em\" role=\"img\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M12 2.5H8A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 6.5 4v1H8a3 3 0 0 1 3 3v1.5h1A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 13.5 8V4A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 12 2.5M11 11h1a3 3 0 0 0 3-3V4a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H8a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v1H4a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v4a3 3 0 0 0 3 3h4a3 3 0 0 0 3-3zM4 6.5h4A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 9.5 8v4A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 8 13.5H4A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 2.5 12V8A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 4 6.5\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg>Copy Markdown</button><button data-slot=\"button\" class=\"button button--icon-only button--md button--tertiary\" data-rac=\"\" type=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" aria-expanded=\"false\" id=\"react-aria-_R_kminpfsnmknb_\" data-react-aria-pressable=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"button-group__separator\" data-slot=\"button-group-separator\"></span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down text-fd-muted-foreground size-3.5 transition-transform\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button></div></div></div><p class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground text-md mb-4 mt-2\">A composable AI prompt composer with attachments, toolbar actions, send states, queued prompts, and drag-and-drop support.</p><div class=\"mb-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><a class=\"button button--tertiary relative gap-2 dark:bg-default/70 button--sm\" href=\"https://storybook.heroui.pro/?path=/docs/components-ai-promptinput--docs\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"1em\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" width=\"1em\" class=\"text-lg text-[#ff4785]\"><g><path d=\"M356.5,5.2L353.9,63c-0.1,3.2,3.7,5.2,6.3,3.2l22.6-17.1L401.9,64c2.5,1.7,5.8,0,6-3l-2.2-58.8l28.4-2.2   c14.7-1,27.3,10.8,27.3,25.6v460.8c0,14.7-12.3,26.3-26.9,25.6L91.1,496.6c-13.3-0.6-24.1-11.3-24.5-24.7l-16-422.3   c-0.8-14.2,9.9-26.3,24.1-27.1L356.2,4.7L356.5,5.2z M291,198.4c0,10,67.4,5.1,76.6-1.7c0-68.2-36.7-104.3-103.6-104.3   c-67.2,0-104.5,36.8-104.5,91.6c0,94.9,128,96.6,128,148.4c0,15-6.8,23.5-22.4,23.5c-20.5,0-28.8-10.4-27.7-46.1   c0-7.7-77.8-10.3-80.4,0c-5.7,86,47.6,110.9,108.7,110.9c59.6,0,106.1-31.7,106.1-89.1c0-101.7-130.1-99-130.1-149.3   c0-20.7,15.4-23.4,24.1-23.4c9.7,0,26.7,1.5,25.4,39.8L291,198.4z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></g></svg>Storybook</a></div></section><div class=\"prose flex-1 prose-sm\"><h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"usage\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#usage\" class=\"peer\">Usage</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>Use <code>PromptInput</code> as the message composer for chat and agent interfaces.</p>\n"}, {"type": "demo", "slug": "prompt-input-default"}, {"type": "html", "html": "\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"secondary\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#secondary\" class=\"peer\">Secondary</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>Use the secondary variant when the composer sits on a default surface.</p>\n"}, {"type": "demo", "slug": "prompt-input-secondary"}, {"type": "html", "html": "\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"inline\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#inline\" class=\"peer\">Inline</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>Use the inline variant for a compact, cursor-style composer that keeps attachment, input, and send on one row. It expands to the stacked layout when text wraps to a second line or attachments are added.</p>\n"}, {"type": "demo", "slug": "prompt-input-inline"}, {"type": "html", "html": "\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"with-suggestions\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#with-suggestions\" class=\"peer\">With Suggestions</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>Compose <code>PromptInput</code> with <code>PromptSuggestion</code> to create a landing-style composer with quick-start prompts.</p>\n"}, {"type": "demo", "slug": "prompt-input-with-suggestions"}, {"type": "html", "html": "\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"run-state\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#run-state\" class=\"peer\">Run State</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>Prompt input supports <code>submitted</code>, <code>streaming</code>, <code>ready</code>, and <code>error</code> states for send/stop behavior.</p>\n"}, {"type": "demo", "slug": "prompt-input-run-state"}, {"type": "html", "html": "\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"queue\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#queue\" class=\"peer\">Queue</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>Use <code>PromptInput.Queue</code> to show queued follow-up prompts in a compact card above the composer shell. Place it as a sibling of <code>PromptInput.Shell</code> inside <code>PromptInput</code>. Keep queue rows text-only for a clean surface — store attachments in your queue model and restore them to <code>PromptInput.Attachments</code> when the user edits a queued prompt.</p>\n"}, {"type": "demo", "slug": "prompt-input-queue"}, {"type": "html", "html": "\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"with-attachments\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#with-attachments\" class=\"peer\">With Attachments</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>Pair <code>PromptInput</code> with <code>ChatAttachmentInput.Dropzone</code> to accept dropped files. While a file is dragged over the shell, the composer shows a dotted accent border.</p>\n"}, {"type": "demo", "slug": "chat-attachment-composer"}, {"type": "html", "html": "\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"anatomy\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#anatomy\" clas